<br/>狼大，半导体设备持仓有什么建议不，谢谢狼大&amp;#128591;[/quote]<br/>ETF持仓  个股方面我主要做材料", "lou": 1921, "content_length": 32, "reply_to": 863962186, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1775703127}, {"pid": 863967111, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 39, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-04-09 11:20", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "我TM最近是有点霉运在身上<br/>2选1都是选到弱的那个。。。。。。。。。。", "lou": 1922, "content_length": 64, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1775704821}, {"pid": 863968176, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 22, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-04-09 11:27", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "[quote][pid=863967890,45974302,3571]Reply[/pid] [b]Post by [uid=38534514]晨星233[/uid] (2026-04-09 11:25):[/b]<br/><br/>狼大，创新药是补跌吗？[/quote]<br/>对啊  等下一次套利机会吧  他不是主线。", "lou": 1923, "content_length": 39, "reply_to": 863967890, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1775705234}, {"pid": 863969659, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 13, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-04-09 11:36", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "[quote][pid=863968663,45974302,3571]Reply[/pid] [b]Post by [uid=67152095]xiaoh1992[/uid] (2026-04-09 11:30):[/b]<br/><br/>但按狼大你习惯应该是平铺吧？[/quote]<br/><br/>这种情况很难平铺 看不过来", "lou": 1924, "content_length": 29, "from_client": "8 Android", "reply_to": 863968663, "postdatetimestamp": 1775705804}, {"pid": 863971688, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 17, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-04-09 11:50", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "[quote][pid=863970298,45974302,3572]Reply[/pid] [b]Post by [uid=65490615]子午卯酉甲乙丙丁[/uid] (2026-04-09 11:41):[/b]<br/><br/>狼大，上午缩量1200亿，但是白线在上。今天机构的目标是兜住指数然后再冲一次4020-4030把筹码派发出去么？[/quote]<br/><br/>白线在上怎么派发 你会买吗 我肯定不买啊", "lou": 1925, "content_length": 41, "from_client": "8 Android", "reply_to": 863970298, "postdatetimestamp": 1775706637}, {"pid": 863974791, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 48, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-04-09 12:13", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "今天白线在上 肯定没有买点<br/>下午不管涨还是跌 我都会找个地方减回50%-55%仓位 我昨天没有减 今天会减<br/>目前持仓方向  半导体材料  商航 国算<br/>我只会在我的体系确定性位置减<br/>不是最高 也不是最低  而是最确定<br/><br/>就像创新药一样 我没空去研究那边的基本面 我就只按纯技术 到位置买 到位置卖就行。没到位置就不操作。", "lou": 1926, "content_length": 267, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1775708019}, {"pid": 863976887, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 41, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-04-09 12:31", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "今天在水下的时间太长了 而且没有明显缩量 ，对比之前2WE以下就是放量 <br/>证明换手不小，为什么在水下换手，肯定有问题<br/><br/>不过我会在10号之后买回这部分仓位 我和机构一起避一下", "lou": 1927, "content_length": 155, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1775709092}, {"pid": 863979708, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 25, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-04-09 12:57", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "今天白线在上 银保证还在杀 证明这里肯定不可能是反转位 那就仍然按之前的策略做 <br/>该激进的时候激进 该保守的时候保守", "lou": 1928, "content_length": 104, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1775710637}, {"pid": 863980093, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 26, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-04-09 13:01", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "[quote][pid=863979749,45974302,3575]Reply[/pid] [b]Post by [uid=39810331]a471428019[/uid] (2026-04-09 12:57):[/b]<br/><br/>这个位子太吓人了早盘我的创新药+6隔一会看-10这谁受的了吗的[/quote]<br/>在错的时候做错的事情", "lou": 1929, "content_length": 25, "reply_to": 863979749, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1775710875}, {"pid": 863980903, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 36, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-04-09 13:09", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "[quote][pid=863980630,45974302,3575]Reply[/pid] [b]Post by [uid=4205